label: DRAW
description: a drawings or a map or a diagram

label: DRAW+AF8-L
description: a table or a tabular legend and drawings or a map or a diagram

label: LINE+AF8-HW
description: a table or a filled form of handwritten texts on a page

label: LINE+AF8-P
description: a table or a filled form of printed texts on a document page

label: LINE+AF8-T
description: a table or a filled form of typed texts on a document page

label: PHOTO
description: photos or photo cutouts attached to the document page

label: PHOTO+AF8-L
description: a table or a tabular legend and photos or photo cutouts on a document page

label: TEXT
description: printed and handwritten text styles on a page like a newspaper cutout or a book cutout commented in another way

label: TEXT+AF8-HW
description: a handwritten plain text or handwritten text paragraphs on a page

label: TEXT+AF8-P
description: a printed plain text or printed text paragraphs or printed list items on a document page

label: TEXT+AF8-T
description: a typed plain text or typed text paragraphs or typed list items on a document page
